{"tid":911603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"裕株缺席一個月GFRIEND公司持續賣關子","createTime":"2018-11-22T04:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T13:52:53.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"755c8c9d8e70abb84e6ca4dea7482fc9b0384392","tid":911603,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/08/1802270353452122-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F1802270353452122-600x400.jpg&h=cf874f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國人氣女團GFRIEND訪台記者會資料照，右一為Yuju裕株。<br />\n<br />\n韓國人氣女團GFRIEND成員Yuju（裕株），自10月底開始缺席團體活動，近日的官方行程表也都寫出&ldquo;裕株不參與活動&rdquo;，引髮粉絲擔憂。今（20）日下午，其所屬經紀公司Source Music表示，近日將會告知大家裕株缺席活動的原因。<br />\n<br />\n由於Source Music自10月底就一直未回應此事，讓許多粉絲擔心裕株 &ldquo;是否失踪&rdquo;等問題。今日其公司表示&ldquo;裕株的人身安全完全沒有問題（ 유 주 의 신 변 에 는 아 무 런 문 제 가 없 다 ）&rdquo;，但仍未告訴大家裕株缺席活動的原因，僅表示近日會公佈此事。<br />\n<br />\n裕株近日最後一次參與GFRIEND的公開行程，已是10月27日的事。但在11月9日公開的《月刊尹鐘信》的訪談中，被問及&ldquo;今後的計劃&rdquo;時，裕株曾表示：&ldquo;會以GFRIEND成員的身份好好的準備很棒的活動，希望大家能守護我！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n為此，也有粉絲認為，&ldquo;會不會只是要推出驚喜新作所以暫時賣關子？&rdquo;，但也有粉絲對於長時間無法得知裕株的消息、公司又遲遲不給出具體回應而擔憂。本日Source Music透露裕株並無安全疑慮，也先讓部分粉絲鬆了一口氣。<br />\n<br />\n有小道消息指，GFRIEND已確認將在下年一月回歸，而成員Yuju缺席活動的原因是為準備將發行的正式專輯作曲作詞。"},{"pid":"4ce90c74cea7604a4472d5ed23d671ebb22baf68","tid":911603,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:48:48.000Z","msg":"ptt好似有講佢12月會出返嚟"},{"pid":"856a77c409d6953acfc1dfd285fb6e9e070f1921","tid":911603,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4ce90c74cea7604a4472d5ed23d671ebb22baf68","tid":911603,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:48:48.000Z","msg":"ptt好似有講佢12月會出返嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:18:16.000Z","msg":"GFriend的Yuju將從12月開始進行正常活動. <br />\n<br />\nGFriend所屬公司Source Music 22日表示:&quot;Yuju沒有任何問題,計劃從12月開始正常活動.&quot; <br />\n<br />\n個公告咁短既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7b0ce101f9e0662e2572fdbb975c36c72e4894","tid":911603,"uid":3405,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:24:12.000Z","msg":"乳豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae633775cd0d94f02a3e8194357abd11501ffd0d","tid":911603,"uid":76098,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:27:30.000Z","msg":"會唔會係呢排人氣下滑想做新聞ja  <br />\n利申 非串"},{"pid":"e205428598cb5687b9a246481dddd231d48ff632","tid":911603,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae633775cd0d94f02a3e8194357abd11501ffd0d","tid":911603,"uid":76098,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:27:30.000Z","msg":"會唔會係呢排人氣下滑想做新聞ja  <br />\n利申 非串"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:36:59.000Z","msg":"唔係幾覺會影響人氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824ce11e5f927b4dca7f05a86b36108242ced4d1","tid":911603,"uid":171594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"希望係準備緊solo"},{"pid":"4c765312d54e073ee201d646875d0a2a32b5bd86","tid":911603,"uid":80792,"like":12,"dislike":12,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:50:17.000Z","msg":"一係整容失敗一係大肚"},{"pid":"34a8f8b7569dc2e08a61ce629dda86aca89af680","tid":911603,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:51:41.000Z","msg":"那個來"},{"pid":"bf06b94ea70a1b209f0382903b3866a9f52adbc5","tid":911603,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:54:15.000Z","msg":"落緊仔"},{"pid":"d61a5d8369133ec5f2405e7575b7af7f216539a3","tid":911603,"uid":2781,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講個合理啲嘅解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown